column5: The latest In-fisherman Magazine has a very good and familiar picture in the 2-page "Adventures" section showing Jared (Obabikon) with a dandy muskie taken near the reef just west of his camp. Nice picture, Jared! Bill Krejca
thanks guys! I haven't seen it yet. Just trying to get the resort going up here! Finally have internet!
Congrates on the fish and the picture in the mag...
